OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FThe England team were visited by
OL,7,Fofficers from the UK Football Policing
OL,8,FUnit at their training base, ITV News
OL,9,FSports Editor Steve Scott and Producer
OL,10,FJoe Wardropper report
OL,12,FEngland's men's footballers have been
OL,13,Fbriefed on how police are cracking
OL,14,Fdown on racist social media abuse
OL,15,Fahead of next month's Euros in Germany.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/10
