OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FChief Constable Mark Roberts, the
OL,7,Fnational lead for policing football,
OL,8,Fsaid officers were conscious of the
OL,9,F"horrendous abuse" directed at some
OL,10,Fblack players after England's defeat
OL,11,Fin the final of the 2020 European
OL,12,FChampionships.
OL,14,F"We spoke to the squad and reassured
OL,15,Fthem that we treated it seriously...
OL,16,F(and) explained the reporting
OL,17,Fmechanism to the players," he said.
