OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FThe England team were visited by
OL,7,Fofficers from the UK Football Policing
OL,8,FUnit at their training base at St
OL,9,FGeorge's Park earlier this year and
OL,10,Fadvised on how to block abusive
OL,11,Fcontent.
OL,13,F"It's appalling," Mr Roberts said.
OL,14,F"You think about the consequences for
OL,15,Fthe player's families. What if the
OL,16,Fchildren see it?"
OL,18,FThe FA's head of security Steve Lewis
OL,19,Fsaid the England players "listened
OL,20,Fintently" to the briefing.
