OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FCo-operation with social media
OL,7,Fcompanies around online abuse
OL,8,Fcompanies had also "improved
OL,9,Fmassively", Roberts revealed.
OL,11,FFirms had previously been "shoddy" and
OL,12,Fslow in handing over evidence in the
OL,13,Ftime window necessary for police to
OL,14,Fprosecute suspects under the Malicious
OL,15,FCommunications Act, he told ITV News.
OL,17,FBut companies were now acting much
OL,18,Fmore quickly: ''I have no complaints,
OL,19,Fthey seem keen to work with us",
OL,20,FRoberts said.
