OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FAround 300,000 England fans are
OL,7,Fexpected to travel to the European
OL,8,FChampionships in Germany, in what is
OL,9,Fbeing described as the most accessible
OL,10,Ffootball tournament in years.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a media briefing at the
OL,13,FForeign and Commonwealth Office on
OL,14,FTuesday, Roberts revealed that the
OL,15,Fnumber of football banning orders
OL,16,Fissued to supporters ahead of Euro 24
OL,17,Fhad risen to 2,000.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/10
