OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FFans subject to banning orders are
OL,7,Fforced to surrender their passports
OL,8,Ffor the duration of the competition,
OL,9,Fin order to minimise the risk of
OL,10,Fhooliganism.
OL,12,FBut police stressed that England fans
OL,13,Fshould be judged on their behaviour in
OL,14,Frecent tournaments, not their
OL,15,Freputations.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/10
