OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,F"The vast majority of our fans travel
OL,7,Fto all sorts of places and don't get
OL,8,Fthemselves into trouble", Roberts
OL,9,Fsaid, pointing to a total of two
OL,10,Farrests at the Russia World Cup in
OL,11,F2018 and none at all in Qatar four
OL,12,Fyears later.
OL,14,FBut the 2020 Euros, delayed a year
OL,15,Fbecause of Covid, were marred by
OL,16,Fscenes of chaos at the final at
OL,17,FWembley, where dozens were detained
OL,18,Fafter ticketless fans stormed the
OL,19,Fturnstiles.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/10
