OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FGerman police present at the briefing
OL,7,Fwarned that "grossly offensive
OL,8,Fbehaviour" would not be tolerated.
OL,10,F"There is of course a red line you
OL,11,Fshouldn't cross because in Germany we
OL,12,Fhave hard restrictions about breaking
OL,13,Fthe law if you do certain behaviour
OL,14,Frelating to the Second World War... If
OL,15,Fyou do this you should fear the
OL,16,Fconsequences", Senior Chief
OL,17,FSuperintendent Oliver Studhoff told
OL,18,FITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/10
