OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FBut Chief Constable Roberts stressed
OL,7,Fthat shared cultural sensitivities
OL,8,Fwould reduce the risk of a
OL,9,Fmisunderstanding between German police
OL,10,Fand English fans.
OL,12,F"Germany is not an entirely dissimilar
OL,13,Fculture, the Germans like a beer, they
OL,14,Fare used to people having a drink," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/10
