OL,3,CEuros 2024: Tougher antiracism police
OL,4,Cprotection for England squad
OL,6,FBut Roberts admitted police would have
OL,7,Fto "live with" the decision by UK
OL,8,Fcourts to lift the football banning
OL,9,Forder imposed on the far-right
OL,10,Factivist and self-proclaimed "football
OL,11,Fhooligan" Tommy Robinson.
OL,13,F"We're not naive, we'll have people
OL,14,Fout there", he said.
